Located next to ziv center (7 mins):
Address - Azar St. 6, 2nd floor
5 mins by bus or 15 mins walking from Technion main gate,
15 mins walk from Grand kanyon
Monthly rent - 2.5k ILS
Arnona - ~500 ILS every 2 months
Availability - May 12 (flexible)
The apartment is quite big and can be shared with another flatmate. A table can fit into the balcony for smoking and coffee. Both is also fine.
It comes with a desk, 2 closets (one per room), fridge, a washing machine a tv and a gas kitchen. The AC is present in both rooms.
The contract will end in mid August and should be renewed for another year.

If you are interested, pls write me in private.
